These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, swimming, soccer, golf
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the car and the person driving the motorbike##2
6. the person who's sport is golf is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | golf | lacrosse     | soccer | swimming |
| Transport     | bike     | motorbike | roller  | car      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop, rock, techno
House: farmhouse, colonial, cape-cod, wooden
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the colonial house##1
2. the wooden house is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the wooden house##1
4. the wooden house is on the right of the colonial house##1
5. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
6. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop    | techno     | rock  |
| House     | farmhouse    | cape-cod | colonial | wooden |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, bridge, whist
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, rabbit, snake
1. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
2. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person playing whist##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Game   | snooker   | bridge   | monopoly  | whist |
| Pet           | lizard | snake | rabbit | cat  |

