.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, march, august, december
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, egyptian, indian
1. the indian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in july and the egyptian##2
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
4. the egyptian is on the left or right of the indian##3
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the argentine is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Birthday         | march | july | december | august  |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | argentine   | indian  | egyptian |

