.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, emerald, green, blue
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, roller, train, tram
1. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes green##1
2. the person driving the train is between the person driving the tram and the person who likes green##2
3. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the train and the person who likes lavender##2
4. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Color    | lavender | green | blue | emerald |
| Transport   | roller | boat  | train    | tram  |

