.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, filmmaking, fishing
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, almond-milk, milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | fishing | filmmaking | board-games | drawing   |
| Beverage   | sprite | almond-milk | soy-milk      | milk |

