The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile, taxi, tram
1. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
2. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the tram is the person traveling to nizza##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
5. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
6. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| City       | san-francisco | nizza | hannover    | london      |
| Transport   | taxi       | tram       | snowmobile | skateboard |

