.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, german, turkish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, rose, azalea, dahlia
1. the canadian is on the far right##1
2. the american is the american##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
4. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the canadian##3
5. the german is on the left or right of the turkish##3
6. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the turkish##3
7. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | american | german  | turkish | canadian |
| Flower           | azalea     | dahlia | poppy    | rose     |

