.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, dannemann, blend, cain
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, manager, musician
1. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the librarian##3
2. the librarian is on the right of the manager##1
3. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the bartender##1
4. the librarian is on the far left or far right##3
5. the blend-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Cigar   | dannemann  | chaman | cain  | blend      |
| Job    | musician | bartender | manager | librarian |

