1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
4. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
5. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
