.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, mirinda, almond-milk
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, guinea-pig, hamster
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking water is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person drinking almond-milk and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Beverage   | mirinda | water  | iced-tea  | almond-milk |
| Pet           | cat    | hamster | guinea-pig | dog |

