.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-19::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, papaya, plum, pumpkin
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, card-games, rock-climbing, gardening
1. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person eating plum##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Food   | pumpkin        | orange       | plum   | papaya |
| Hobby    | gardening | rock-climbing | card-games | puzzles  |

